      <title>南非的兰特受到关税，政治的双重打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/south-africa-s-rand-suffers-double-blow-from-tariffs-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非兰特（Rand）在周五对美元持续下降，这是因为担心全球统治联盟的全球贸易战争和不稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/south-africa-s-rand-suffers-double-blow-from-tariffs-politics</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 11:20:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
