      <title>鲁贝尼在特朗普变成“理性”之前看到了更多的市场下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/roubini-sees-more-market-declines-before-trump-turns-rational</link>
      <description><![CDATA[努里尔·鲁贝尼（Nouriel Roubini）预测，随着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）拨打他的全球贸易攻击，股市更正可能会加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/roubini-sees-more-market-declines-before-trump-turns-rational</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 11:00:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EM资产随着中国的报复而受到打击，LATAM货币带头损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/emerging-currencies-gain-in-asia-as-tariff-woes-weigh-on-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉丁美洲的货币周五跌倒，智利和墨西哥比索带来的损失和新兴股票跌落，因为在中国宣布卖出泰特（Tit-Tat）措施之后，美国征收美国关税的后果延长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/emerging-currencies-gain-in-asia-as-tariff-woes-weigh-on-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 08:32:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
